Description: Castle Falkreath is a mod that adds a castle in Falkreath

Features:
.Walled in property with castle and gate
.Smithing Facilities
.Scenic viewing areas
.Small planted garden
.Archery range
.Tons of alchemy ingredients
.Small livestock area
.Apiary
.Open bar
.kitchen
.bedroom
.crafting room Alchemy staff and enchanter
.stairs up to roof with archers fort on top of castle
.Throne
.Large Dining area
.Storage all over
.Talos shrine
.Indoor nature/Kynareth shrine
.and much much more

Requirements: Dawnguard,Hearthfire,Dragonborn

i am still new to modding so some things might not be perfect
